      "options": {
        "content": "### Game schema (`game`)\nEach panel below maps **one** `game.*` table (`SELECT *`, latest rows first).\n\n**Parsed** log tables fill **after** a session completes the Loki batch + `log_parser.py`. **CS2KZ** tables fill when SQLite ingest is enabled.\n\nUse **Quick counts** to see whether `ops` has raw lines but `game` is still empty.",
